    "body": "Problem: fg_indexed/bg_indexed were dropped from nvim_get_hl output due to a wrong short_keys guard. HL_FG_INDEXED also wasn't cleared in hl_blend_attrs, and HLATTRS_DICT_SIZE was too small.\r\n\r\nSolution: Remove the short_keys guard, clear HL_FG_INDEXED in hl_blend_attrs, bump HLATTRS_DICT_SIZE to 24, and clarify docs that these flags mean rgb is an approximation of the cterm palette index.\r\n\r\n\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-04-20T09:12:53Z",
